  "description": "A compatibility mod for RPG Parties that adds full Tough as Nails support!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />RPG Parties - Tough As Nails </strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Party up with your friends! Now with Tough as Nails Support!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> <strong> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/mod%20loader-forge-1976d2?style=flat-square\" width=\"112\" height=\"20\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/environment-both-4caf50?style=flat-square\" width=\"112\" height=\"20\" /> <img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/version-1.18.2,%201.16.5,%201.12.2-4caf50?style=flat-square\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"20\" /> </strong> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/rpg-parties\"> <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"> <em> <strong>THIS MOD REQUIRES RPG PARTIES 2.4.0 TO WORK.</strong> </em> </span> </a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mods allows for all 2.4.0+ versions of RPG Parties to support Tough as Nails, allowing you to see your friend's thirst bar! <br />It integrates seamlessly into the party UI so don't worry about it looking weird.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> <strong>Can I use this in a modpack? <br /> </strong>Of course! I don't mind. <br /> <br /> <a href=\"https://client.kinetichosting.net/aff.php?aff=38\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1057333762347778240/1057477061465350265/MATTS.png\" /> </a> <br /> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/G6HrJk7BBc\"> <img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/logopedia/images/0/05/Discord.svg\" width=\"144\" height=\"39\" /> </a> &nbsp;</a></p>",
